item.description: Here's a new location to me. According to the recorded message at Moseley's, the doors open at 7:30pm(lol, I will try to be there at 7:30). Beatlejuice starts at 8:30pm, with two 90 minute sets. This is a +21 event :(. Tickets are $15 at the door. The 36 bus drops off it looks like about a 1/4 mile away(and runs until 1:00am). They probably have a ton of parking(given that it's a big hall). The recorded message states "dress code is casual but neat".
item.how_to_find_us: I have a meetup button/will give out Cell Phone # the night before.
item.name: Beatlejuice in Dedham/on the Boston line 10/27 at 8:00
